lead_paragraph: Both No. 10 Texas A&M and Mississippi will start backup quarterbacks on Saturday when they meet after Aggies starter Trevor Knight and Rebels starter Chad Kelly both suffered serious injuries last week.

headline.print_headline: Texas A&M and Ole Miss Both Look to Backup QBs This Week
headline.main: Texas A&M and Ole Miss Both Look to Backup QBs This Week
